summaries.short: On election night, Vern gets crafty to ensure smooth live coverage, and Deanna struggles to find voices from both parties.​
summaries.full: On election night, the team gets creative to ensure their live coverage goes off without a hitch, and Deanna winds up hosting with vocal Republican Vern, despite her efforts to strike a neutral tone. After the results are announced, Vern worries about the future of his business, but his mood is lifted when a potential advertiser calls from Las Vegas.
